name: Road to Redemption
description:
Road to redemption is a window to a virtual world, where the barrier of the 4th dimension is broken, creating a very realistic illusory effect where the aim is to submerge the viewer and make him part of it, so that he can find his own way to the truth and find his own freedom.

Virtual world
